item_name: Multifunction Baby Adult Children Digital Body Forehead Ear Infrared Thermometer
item_description:
Features:
100% Brand New.
Operate with one button, very simple to use
Green back light, easy to read screen.
A different beep sound would be made when a fever happen.
You should pay attention to your and your families's body temperature.
Suitable for both infants and adults
 
Product Properties:
Style:Handheld
Display Type:Digital
Style:HandheldTheory:Infrared Thermometer
Resolution:.0.1 Deg.C
Material:ABS,Electronic Components
Theory:Infrared Thermometer
Occasion:Car,Home,Office,School
Power Type:Button Battery(Not included)
Measurement range: 0 to 100°C (32 to 212°F)
Accuracy: 0.2°C (body) and 0.5°C (object)

How To Use :
Mode One: For Forhead
1. Match the probe cover and a smile symbol will be displayed on the LCD;
2. Put the thermometer to the temple(touch the skin) and press the button constantly;
3. Keep the thermometer moving along the forehead slowly to the temple on other side.;
4. Release the button then the measurement is completed.

Mode Two: For Ear (±0.2℃)
1. Remove the probe cover;
2. Put the probe lens in the ear properly, and press the button for measurement for one second;
3. Release the button.

Mode Three: For Object(±2℃)
1. Match the probe cover and no smile symbol should be displayed on the LCD;
2. Put the thermometer to the object at 1cm;
3. Press the button for measurement for one second.
4. Release the button.

Note: 1. Mode One is the same to the Mode Three. But the data for forhead measurement may be inaccurate. So this mode is not recommended. Ear Measurement is the most accurate for body temperature measuring. 
2. Other factors also do influence to the measurement.
 
Specifications:
Length: 120mm
Net weight:80g
 
Packing Content:
1 x 8-in-1 Forehead Ear Infrared Thermometer

item_description:

Can use breast pump in the following circumstances:
1.Release of mammary duct blockage or milk deposition.
2.When the baby begins to practice sucking the nipple.

4.Low weight infants can not suck when.
5.When the sick baby sucking force is insufficient.
6.When mother is ill, she needs to keep her milk.

9.There is a need to squeeze the milk directly into the mouth of the baby.

1.Suction bra with high strength materials (imported food grade polycarbonatePP Made, non-toxic tasteless, with milk bottle, can be convenient to breast feeding, especially suitable for professional women to use.

3.Humanized design, in the bell plus soft silicone gasket, sucking comfort.
Usage method:
1.Before use, please clean the ball and the parts of the connecting pipe, and put them into the water to boil.1-2Minutes, dry standby.
2.The bottle body selected sucking cover, then the hose and a suction ball is connected to the pump cover tail protrusion.
3.Wipe the nipple with clean gauze and warm water, place the mammary gland to block.
4.The sucking hood covers the breast and slightly tilted downward, close to. A hand holding the bottle, a hand to squeeze the rubber ball, can suck the milk. In the process of using, the negative pressure can be adjusted according to the number of the balls to be pressed.
5.The sucking end or high pressure, pressure and suction bra breast at the contact point of the hand, to enter the air, you can remove the suction cover.
6.After the next election suck the milk, milk bottle, the nipple is arranged on, feeding the baby can be sucked milk bottle into the refrigerator to be installed, easy to feed, especially for female occupation.

item_name: 30PCS Breast Milk Storage Bag Baby Food Storage 200ml Disposable Freezer Bags
item_description:
Malaysia Post:Receive in 15-25 days
Product Features:
Dual-track design, easy to record, stand-up design, easy to store, BPA free.
How to use:
1. Tear off along the bag tear line after washing your hands
2. Tear the sealing zipper (avoid the fingers to touch the inner wall of the storage bag, do not blow inward)
3. Fix the sealing with your hands, carefully pour into the breast milk, put the bottom in the flat place, so as not to spill
4. Push the remaining part out the air from the bottom to up after pouring
5. Press it to seal (can be repeated several times to ensure that it is fasten off or sealed)
6. Write the date and time down, it can be saved
Note:
1. When heating breast milk, do not use boiled or microwave to heat.
2. The best temperature of waterproof heating is 50-60 degrees, the breast milk will be separated after heating (due to breast milk has not been homogenization, so it is a normal phenomenon).
3. When storing in a refrigerator, please store it in an upright position.
4. Thaw frozen breast milk out before heating, and can not be frozen twice.
5. This product is a disposable item, do not reuse it.
6. This product is sterilized by the Y radiation, it may be a little smell, but not affect the use.
Product Parameters:
1. Material: PE
2. Available colors: Color as shown in Figure
3. Capacity: 200ML
4. Suitable period: lactation
5. Product Description: Disposable
